# Machine Loan Manager

A lightweight web app to track machine loans and reservations.

## Features
- Machine inventory
- Loan tracking
- Reservation management
- Overdue alerts

## Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express
- SQLite

## Installation

git clone https://github.com/yourname/machine-loan-manager

cd machine-loan-manager

npm install

npm start

Open http://localhost:3000
